#. <section class="sutta" id="sn22.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Bhāravagga"
msgstr "3. The Burden"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 24. Abhijānasutta → parijānaṃ (or abhijānaṃ) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Abhijānasutta"
msgstr "24. Directly Knowing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.27"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn22.24:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo "
"dukkhakkhayāya;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, without directly knowing and completely understanding form, "
"without dispassion for it and giving it up, you can’t end suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.3"
msgid ""
"vedanaṃ anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya;"
msgstr "Without directly knowing and completely understanding feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.4"
msgid "saññaṃ anabhijānaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.5"
msgid ""
"saṅkhāre anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya;"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.6"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya."
msgstr ""
"consciousness, without dispassion for it and giving it up, you can’t end "
"suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.7"
msgid ""
"Rūpañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo "
"dukkhakkhayāya;"
msgstr ""
"By directly knowing and completely understanding form, having dispassion for "
"it and giving it up, you can end suffering."

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.8"
msgid "vedanaṃ abhijānaṃ …"
msgstr "By directly knowing and completely understanding feeling …"

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.9"
msgid "saññaṃ …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.10"
msgid "saṅkhāre …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn22.24:1.11"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"consciousness, having dispassion for it and giving it up, you can end "
"suffering.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.24:1.12"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
